{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"38b9bfde94","title":"诗——给沉浸在会议里的人们","origin":"石天河〈逝川忆语——《星星》诗祸亲历记〉，二零零九年十二月，《往事微痕》丛书。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cb863505a9","index":0,"year":1957,"month":2,"day":null,"articleId":"38b9bfde94"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5385632469","name":"王志杰"},{"id":"a185c9b36c","name":"四川"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5c577b2ed0","type":"title","text":"诗——给沉浸在会议里的人们","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"42bacc7729","type":"authors","text":"四川王志杰","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"41c2ce3e2f","type":"subtitle","text":"（王志杰：《新自贡报》文艺编辑）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"c18daf4403","type":"paragraph","text":"一包香烟，一杯浓茶","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"402d70b8ea","type":"paragraph","text":"一盆炉火，一串哈哈……","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"8de8a517a0","type":"paragraph","text":"啊，可怕，可怕","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"aac12b53aa","type":"paragraph","text":"你们满口废话","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"84419c4ed2","type":"paragraph","text":"在会议室里虚度年华","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"2a40072ddd","type":"paragraph","text":"工人将优质产品献给了祖国","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"5aa00aca1c","type":"paragraph","text":"农民献给祖国又一个金色的丰收","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"f9d01c7d9e","type":"paragraph","text":"可你们献给祖国的是什么","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"fe65ace9e2","type":"paragraph","text":"一连串废话，一地的烟头","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"b993a1d9d8","type":"paragraph","text":"如果生命是珍珠","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"290346b80c","type":"paragraph","text":"会议便是大海","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"f12fe902fa","type":"paragraph","text":"它正汹涌着无情的波涛","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"cfe600019e","type":"paragraph","text":"将那闪烁的岁月","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"05eebd8a55","type":"paragraph","text":"深深掩埋","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"b090d4701b","type":"paragraph","text":"沉浸在会议里的人们","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"51748a6b72","type":"paragraph","text":"瞧，你们的嘴唇已结上茧巴","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"e98ec84077","type":"paragraph","text":"会议是一个吝啬的穷鬼","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"c65e8ff4b5","type":"paragraph","text":"它什么也不会给你留下","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"0855f2456c","type":"paragraph","text":"它绝不会给你社会主义大厦","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"38addf573f","type":"paragraph","text":"给你的","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"},{"id":"e1087a3a84","type":"paragraph","text":"顶多是一头白发","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94"}],"page":{"id":"e15c5f2e8b","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"38b9bfde94","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}